Titolo: Calvino Noir

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Calvino Noir is a stealth game developed and published by Calvino Noir, Ltd. It was released on August 25, 2015 for PlayStation 4, August 26, 2015 for Windows and Mac OS X, and August 27, 2015 for iOS.
It received a mixed reception from critics, who enjoyed its distinctive film noir art style but criticized its gameplay, such as stealth mechanics and controls.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 51
